content.text: Trial 3/5, Stage 'ytraverse1': Please describe the image and compute the stiffness matrix.

The image highlights a part of a groove structure, specifically where the groove extends primarily along the Y-axis. The red circle marks this section.

For this traversal, we should prioritize high stiffness along the Y-axis while maintaining standard stiffness in the X and Z directions.

### Assumptions
1. High stiffness (250 N/m) along the Y-axis.
2. Lower stiffness (100 N/m) in the X and Z directions.

### Stiffness Matrix
```json
{
  "stiffness_matrix": [
    [100, 0, 0],
    [0, 250, 0],
    [0, 0, 100]
  ]
}
```
